INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES(1106, 166, 'page_title', 'A Little History');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES(1107, 166, '_page_title', 'field_54e16b871e535');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES(1108, 166, 'left_column_about', 'The tale behind this venture started out tragic and, ultimately, ended in sweet redemption. Our fearless founder, Brian Lucas, used to be fat. Like okra fat. He was stuck in a corporate job that offered long, thankless hours with zero regard for personal nutrition. On several occasions when Brian was tirelessly working late at his desk, he was forced to grab dinner from a depressing vending machine in the office break room. His choices were always the same. Cheetos. Zagnut Candy Bars. A pack of Lifesavers. These options were far from life saving. In fact, over the many years on this job Brian poured countless coins in this machine and only received a higher cholesterol level and protruding belly in return.\r\n\r\nHe finally decided he was ready for something different; both in a professional and personal respect. Having an innate entrepreneurial sense, Brian decided to look into why vending machines, which were so often stocked with the same types of products, did not offer any healthy alternatives. ');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES(1109, 166, '_left_column_about', 'field_54e16a993e2de');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES(1110, 166, 'right_column_about', 'He discovered no satisfying answers and immediately sensed an opportunity. That''s when he bought a machine, filled it with luna bars and started talking to schools, offices and gyms about how things could be different. The response was resounding. People want to eat healthier and want more control over their diet.\r\n\r\nOne machine has now turned into a small army of machines in the Chicago-land area. Brian continues to scour the area, ridding environments of their once sad vending options and putting new life into people''s daily snack choices. And, as for Brian, his gut is now gone and he lives by the namesake of his company, Leangreen Healthy Vending.');
